{"tid":2509383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣外交部：中國大陸似乎準備對台灣發動終極一戰","createTime":"2021-04-29T11:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T11:53:02.000Z","uid":125168,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"76d0fd9ad55a4d0d0aa406a995220369e2b5953c","tid":2509383,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432959&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=db083a09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432959&h=1cf177b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432959</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在台灣，外交部長吳釗燮接受英國天空電視台訪問時說，大陸似乎正準備對台灣發動終極一戰。<br />\n<br />\n外交部長吳釗燮：「大陸持續發布虛假訊息（進行）混合戰，近期加強活動打擊台灣，所有這些看來，都是在準備對台發動終極一戰。這是我們的國家，這是我們的人民，這是我們的生活方式，我們將捍衛自己，直到最後。」<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮說，大陸持續向國際社會謊稱，台灣是中華人民共和國的一部分，但事實上，沒有一天統治過台灣。他又指大陸持續對台灣文攻武嚇，除不斷軍事滋擾和威脅外，也利用所謂的一中原則，打壓台灣的國際空間。<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮形容台灣身處大陸威權秩序擴張的最前線，北京如果武力犯台，後果將是全球性的。"},{"pid":"bc06de03f21d5c7c6ab775d6ea2a732f49d80b66","tid":2509383,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6CS330.gif&amp;h=4228923e&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"2ee5e94dc90bbcfda9061b49cabdb9886eee0d57","tid":2509383,"uid":19527,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:31:38.000Z","msg":"真係會打就唔會日日喊打喊殺"},{"pid":"734e24520f833b7af7b62cb6412c08f81d35f545","tid":2509383,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"準備了七十年而已"},{"pid":"1d6811116279481571545acd22f51a000b69e30a","tid":2509383,"uid":100680,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:32: